            <span class="chip"><span class="dot"></span> Friendly Help</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OUR STORY -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="title">
        <h2>Our story</h2>
        <p>Local service with big attention to detail.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="aboutGrid">
        <div class="card aboutCard">
          <h3>Printing, embroidery, and “let’s figure it out” problem-solving.</h3>
          <p>
            We started My Shirt &amp; Signs to help local businesses, schools, and families get great-looking
            print and embroidery without the headache. Whether you have press-ready artwork or a simple idea,
            we’ll guide you to the right materials, finishes, and quantities.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our goal is straightforward: make the process easy, communicate clearly, and deliver quality on time.
            If you’re not sure what you need, that’s okay — we’ll walk through options and recommend what fits your budget.
          </p>
          <p>
            Need something beyond garments? We also help with items like business cards, flyers, banners, and more.
            If it can be printed, there’s a good chance we can do it — and if not, we’ll point you in the right direction.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="facts" aria-label="Quick facts">
          <div class="fact">
